  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0ba3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b86\u0baf\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Chief Administrative Officer of the Pradeshiya Sabha was attacked and killed with a sharp weapon",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Polonnaruwa - A woman chief administrative officer of Lankapura Pradeshiya Sabha was attacked and killed with a sharp weapon, police said.",
        "It is reported that the officer, who sustained severe head injuries in the attack, succumbed to his injuries after being admitted to the hospital.",
        "It is noteworthy that the deceased woman's husband told the investigation that he saw a person in the room of the house but could not identify him due to darkness."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
